    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Sync speed is heavily dependent on diskIO, bandwith and which peers your node connects to. Your nodes are already synced, block import speed depends on CPU and diskIO mainly.\r\nJudging from your logs I don't see any problems, both machines execute well over 100MGas/sec. \r\nThe difference in timing can happen because your nodes have different peers, some that might be closer to the validator that produced the block",
